# EC2 Demo

A small cli util to create and delete EC2 instances.


## Design

ec2-demo create <env> <file.yaml>
ec2-demo list <env>
ec2-demo delete <env> <id>


## Implementation

We will use:

- click for the cli interface
- boto3 for the API calls (SDK)
